author: @jeanettejochebed8405
text: Ryeowook has the uncanny ability to tell such moving stories with his voice. "The Little Prince" and "It's Okay" were so compelling and emotional and Lingering was too. This time Ryeowook tells the story of someone who despite having lost someone, still feels their effects and memories upon that person's very soul. It's a beautiful tale of the emotions one might feel in their day-to-day lives despite appearing normal to others. It's quite beautiful, thank you Ryeowook for this lovely song 💙💙💙
